OL,3,CSocial housing tenants 'coughing up
OL,4,Cblack phlegm' in mouldy home
OL,6,FLaura tells ITV News: "We're literally
OL,7,Fcoughing up black phlegm. In the
OL,8,Fnight, we always think we have a cold
OL,9,Fand then all of a sudden, we go out
OL,10,Ffor a walk and it clears.
OL,12,F"I was ready to get back to work,
OL,13,Fready to get on with life, but it's
OL,14,Fmentally impacted me really badly and
OL,15,Fphysically, I actually deleted the
OL,16,Fpictures (of the mould) because they
OL,17,Fwere so disgusting."
