OL,6,FIn response, Andium Homes says the
OL,7,Fwellbeing of its clients is their
OL,8,Fpriority and they have a dedicated
OL,9,Fteam ready to carry out any work that
OL,10,Fis needed.
OL,12,FDominique Caunce from the social
OL,13,Fhousing provider adds: "It's very
OL,14,Fdifficult when it's mould, humidity,
OL,15,Fcondensation. Brompton Villa is one of
OL,16,Four oldest homes but has got
OL,17,Finsulation and electric heating.
