OL,6,F"It is really important that residents
OL,7,Fmake sure they are ventilating and
OL,8,Fheating their properties in order to
OL,9,Feradicate as much of that moisture as
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,12,F"We have recently installed a PIV unit
OL,13,Fthat will remove a lot of the old
OL,14,Fstagnant air and replace it with fresh
OL,15,Fair.
OL,17,F"We have been, on average, speaking to
OL,18,Fthem twice a week since the New Year.
OL,19,FWe will be going to visit them again
OL,20,Fjust to check in and see how the PIV
OL,21,Funit is working."
