OL,9,Fthey have been repaired several times
OL,10,Fand the organisation will be
OL,11,Finstalling secondary glazing.
OL,13,FShe explains: "(The issues) are likely
OL,14,Fto have developed over a lengthy
OL,15,Fperiod of time where heating and
OL,16,Fventilation just hasn't been at the
OL,17,Fadequate level.
