OL,6,F"We have given advice and are taking
OL,7,Fthose extra steps now by putting in
OL,8,Fthe PIV unit but it takes effort on
OL,9,Fboth sides to keep these homes
OL,10,Fefficient."
OL,12,FPaul and Laura say they are looking to
OL,13,Fmove into a different property but
OL,14,Fhave been told they need to apply to
OL,15,Fthe Affordable Housing Gateway, which
OL,16,Falready has more than 600 households
OL,17,Fon its waiting list.
