OL,6,FIn response to ITV News's story,
OL,7,FJersey's Housing Minister, Deputy Sam
OL,8,FMezec, says: "I have already asked
OL,9,FAndium for an update on what's being
OL,10,Fdone to address the complaints Paul
OL,11,Fand Laura have made. I have also been
OL,12,Fgiven their number to call them so I
OL,13,Fcan ask how I can help them."
